Here, basically we are trying to reduce our search space in our interested side, we will reduce search space left side if we want first index (as array is already sorted) .Similarily , we can say for last index will lie on right side of array

Condition:- 
-->end = mid-1; 
helping us to reduce search space in left side of array , as our interested side if first index

-->start = mid+1
helping us to reduce search space in right side of array , as our interested side if last index

