**Solution 1:**

- If sum of gas is more than sum of cost, then there must be a solution. The question guaranteed that the solution is unique i.e. The first one we found is the right one.
- The tank should never be negative, so restart whenever there is a negative number.

Time complexity: `O(n)`
Space Complexity: `O(1)`

